Does any of my PD twitter followers know if to much sinemet is a bad thing? With the lockdown I have had to take aroud an extra 300mg daily or so as my off periods would be long as hell.

My proper regime should be 150mg 6am 125mg 9am till 9pm and so on totaling = 825mg

My lockdown down regime is 6am 125mg then 9am 125mg then every 2 hrs until 9pm 125mg = 1000mg.

I have alot less off time... I've been on this regime for 4/5 months.. I was going to bring it up when I seen the prof at the clinic but with discussing DBS it slipped my mind

Cheers.
